CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 28, 1957, pg. A1, reads: "New Tipstaff - Shortly after he was sworn in as a tipstaff in Allegheny County Court, Curtis B. Haines.... - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of three men, including one shaking hands with Curtis B. Haines on right, after his swearing in as Allegheny County Court tipstaff, posed in courtroom
